title: Crew Show (Matt, Zack, Vinny)
author: matt@thesmokingtire.com (Matt Farah & Zack Klapman)
itunes:title: Crew Show (Matt, Zack, Vinny)
itunes:author: Matt Farah & Zack Klapman
itunes:summary: Corona virus is having an impact on everyone. Events are canceled, auto shows, races, press launches, not to mention the impact on people's businesses and jobs. We feel for everyone who has and could be effected. But we are not infectious disease specialists. We're car nerds, so we find a way to talk about cars. There's Geneva debuts (good and terrible), whether or not the Gemera will come to America, million dollar safari cars, and a TON of Q&A.
